			<Text>+ 1 [ICON_RES_PERFUME] Perfume luxury. Each source of [ICON_RES_INCENSE] Incense or [ICON_RES_SPICES] Spices worked by this City produces +1 [ICON_GOLD] Gold. Improved [ICON_GOLD] Gold and trade route income to and from this City. No more than 3 may be built.</Text>
