		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_PERFUMERY_PEDIA">
			<Text>Perfume making has been around for at least 4000 years and involved using flowers, spices, oils and other natural products mixed in water to create a pleasant scent. Later developments in Chemistry/Alchemy allowed more subtle and better control and a wider rage of fragrences.</Text>
